data.title: Salvatore Quasimodo Autograph
data.meta_description: Signed card, 5 x 3 inch, signed in blue ballpoint ink "Salvatore Quasimodo", attractively mounted (removable) for display with a photograph, shows Salvatore Quasimodo in a chest-up portrait (altogether 8,25 x 11,75), in very fine condition.
data.text:
Signed card, 5 x 3 inch, signed in blue ballpoint ink "Salvatore Quasimodo", attractively mounted (removable) for display with a photograph, shows Salvatore Quasimodo in a chest-up portrait (altogether 8,25 x 11,75), in very fine condition.

All of our pieces are sold with a Certificate of Authenticity. If a piece turns out to be wrong or if you do not like an autograph, you will get your money back for a lifetime.
